277, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9688363302759027, \"rank\": 0.032166082098635376, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999909481644362, \"rank\": 6.725335157227665e-06, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dress she wore on Thursday evening was described as her best yet by fans when she shared a chic picture of herself and we have to say we agree.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rebecca - who often goes by the nickname Becky - rockeda stunning dress by L.K.Bennett, known as the 'Robyn Green And Red Spot Print Dress' which is part of the luxury high street store's current season.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.9996206609617566, \"rank\": 0.00037948298512034743, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L.K.Bennett\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It costs \\u00a3359, which is a little pricey but as with all L.K.Bennett numbers, the cut is always sublime and what's more, polka dots never go out of style.\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L.K.Bennett\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The website's description of the look could not be more apt: \\\"Crafted from a lightweight and floaty fabric in a green and red spot print, it's a sleeveless, slightly-sheer style with a slip base, and has a round neck with pleat detail, a jaunty side tie, and a midi skirt with an asymmetric tier.\\\"\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My suggestion would be to wear it with a pair of heels and for a summer wedding or a special birthday dinner.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The mother-of-two added tan high heeled espadrilles (this summer shoe is adored by the Princess of Wales and the Duchess of Sussex FYI)and wore her famous blonde locks swept back.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Becky's super chic look was put together bysublime stylistto the stars,Martine Alexander.The talented professional helpfully gave us the lowdown on how you can style polka-dots into your wardrobe.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a rule, I always say make the bold print the main focus of your outfit.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With Becky's LK Bennett dress, we wanted to let the dress speak!\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LK Bennett\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L.K.Bennett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We styled it with anude espadrille from Aspigaand Becky chose to have a simple hair style so her look wasn't too much.\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, if your style is more edgy and you want to make a bold statement, then clash your polka dots with a stripe!\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a simple but very effective way to stand out, for all the right reasons.\\\"\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Martine added: \\\"Using polka dots as an accent in a block colour outfit is an easy way to create some interest without making it too garish, if that's not your personal style.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, a polka dot neck scarf (can also be used as a twilly on your bag), headband, court shoe or pussy bow will just give a nod to the trend without being overkill.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have found a dress or jumpsuit you love that's a very bold polka dot but it's too much for you, layer over with a blazer to tone down the overall look.\\\"\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Supported by Friends Like These\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": []}]}"